Author: peanutbella
Text: YEP lol like I said I didn’t want to do any of this the other day and my therapist was like “I would argue ED is the one who doesn’t want this :)” and I just sat there like :|  like these thoughts are so distorted, the moments of clarity are just flat out confusing. haha

Author: taoshka
Text: Lol I feel like such a doof when my spouse calls me out on my ED "logic." I was bitching that I was hungry at 3pm despite eating at 9 this morning and they were just like, "Babe, you don't just eat once and then you're done forever....We're humans, we have to keep doing it." And I'm sitting there all salty with no comeback
